Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne的发展型？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:50.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Arche Gundam：权天使高达，Throne系列的发展型）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.51,0:23:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这就开战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam之间盛大的战争！
